          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1651581304081-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are in the oven, slice your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> finely</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until golden</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1651581297737-x200.jpg",
