    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are browning, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and set aside until later – these are your <strong>balsamic tomatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
