    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>peppercorn mushrooms</strong> between the<strong> ciabatta bases</strong></p><p>Top with <strong>half </strong>the<strong> balsamic tomatoes</strong>, the <strong>sliced steak</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the<strong> salad </strong>and a <strong>ciabatta lid</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips </strong>with the <strong>remaining balsamic tomatoes </strong>and<strong> salad </strong>to the side and drizzle the dressing over the salad</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
